BUDDING act, Ubi Kimberley Inikpi aka Ubi has released her debut single titled ‘Hapu Ya’. ‘Hapu Ya’ is the lead single off Ubi’s forthcoming debut EP which is scheduled for release in early 2022. The smash-hit single is produced by Beatpriet and Mixed and Mastered by PTDmix. Ubi brings her writing ability to the fore here by penning down this catchy, singalong anthem. Hapu Ua YA Is officially out worldwide and is currently enjoying massive rotation across the hottest radio stations in Nigeria even as Ubi embarks on a media tour soon.   Afri-Classical concert holds 2022 edition on Jan 30     Portable laments excessive demands by sex workers     Go buy credit, Vee teases Laycon over Snapchat call   Read Also: Afri-Classical concert holds 2022 edition on Jan 30 - Advertisement - The Afrofusion singer and songwriter has been passionate about music from a young age. She grew up on a sonic diet of various genres — notably Afrobeats, hip-hop, and R&B. To Ubi, music is freedom; a medium of expressing her true self. For her, the most important aspect of the writing stage is ensuring it comes from an honest place. Ubi makes music for the divine feminine in everyone and is here to cement her place in the next generation of Nigeria’s musical stars.